Name: Hentai Jigsaw Girls 3
About the game: Challenging 6 x 6 jigsaw puzzles featuring hentai girls in summer beach clothing on an anime styled background. Relaxing background music. The game features 12 puzzles with different girls, which you can solve in any order of your choice. There is no time limit, but there is a timer in case you want to see how quickly you can solve each puzzle. Be among the fastest puzzle solvers to achieve a top spot in our Leadrboards.
